data.content:
Anh - Anh
beanbag
■ noun
1》 a small bag filled with dried beans and used in children's games.
2》 a large cushion filled with polystyrene granules, used as a seat.

sentences.en: When i was in the street throwing a beanbag with the other children and mr. Tanaka happened to stroll out of the Seafood company, i always stopped what i was doing to watch him.
sentences.vi: Mỗi khi tôi nô đùa với đứa trẻ khác ngoài đường mà trông thấy ông tanaka từ trong công ty hải sản đi ra, là tôi ngừng chơi để nhìn ông đã.
